00:26:11,664 --> 00:26:13,264
<font color=#FFFF00>Satu juta dolar.</font>

360
00:26:13,694 --> 00:26:15,499
<font color=#FFFF00>Satu juta dolar entah dari mana?</font>

361
00:26:15,538 --> 00:26:17,138
<font color=#FFFF00>Berdasarkan apa?</font>

