00:30:00,819 --> 00:30:03,086
<font color=#FFFF00>aku sedang memikirkan bagaimana memberi kesaksian.</font>

420
00:30:03,437 --> 00:30:04,616
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu?</font>

421
00:30:04,648 --> 00:30:10,314
<font color=#FFFF00>Haruskah aku mulai berbohong tentang fakta bahwa aku
